Raytracer C++ framework for "Introduction to Computer Graphics"
===============================================================

Pierre-Antoine Locatelli, Paul Meunier

To launch the generation of file, just execute exec.bat which is at the root of the project
It's possible to edit it to execute the raytracer on a specific file, just need to change input_file value in the .bat file.

By default, the exec.bat create a .png for each scene file present at the root of the project.

Currently generated:

scene01.yaml -> scene01.png
scene02.yaml -> scene02.png